{
  "stem": "5430.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I-- I was given tools to mark the trees you know, by size and by what kind of a tree it was designated to be, whether it's for lumber, or for rifle butts, or whatever the designation of the tree-- of the wood was.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And so, I would mark the trees with the special chisels at the end of the tree.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And also, I had a-- a wooden board.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I would mark how-- how many trees and what they were doing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "When they cut down the trees, instead of making it 10-feet long, they would make it 10 and 1 inch.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And after I mark it, the end, they would cut the-- the ends off and get a new marking on it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "In other words, so that they almost made like, double their-- their number.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "You had to use all kinds of gimmicks to survive.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There-- there are no guards.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, there's no guards.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had no guards.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had a commander who was in charge of the camp, and another commander who was in charge of the working crews.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He, himself, was a-- was a prisoner.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In other words, the whole community over there, it was all prisoners.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They  couldn't leave either.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But they excelled, supposedly, in-- in what they were doing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were given certain ranks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And for that, we would get-- we would get a-- once a day, a pot of kasha, in the soup.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I think the-- the bread was given out once a week.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And-- and most of the people would eat it up, like, in one day or whatever.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] As far as food is concerned, we were fortunate.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "As a family, and we had our belongings with us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We were able to barter with the local farmers.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
